<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Pago exitoso</title>
  <style>
    :root { --ok:#16a34a; --ink:#111827; --sub:#6b7280; --bg:#f9fafb; --card:#ffffff; }
    body { margin:0; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial; background:var(--bg); color:var(--ink); }
    .wrap { max-width: 720px; margin: 4rem auto; background:var(--card); padding:2rem; border-radius:12px; box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.06); }
    .badge { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:.5rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--ok); }
    .badge svg { width:22px; height:22px; }
    .muted { color:var(--sub); }
    .row { margin:1rem 0; }
    .grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr auto; gap:.5rem 1rem; }
    .btns { display:flex; gap:.75rem; margin-top:1.25rem; flex-wrap:wrap;}
    .btn { padding:.75rem 1rem; border-radius:10px; text-decoration:none; font-weight:600; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; background:#fff; }
    .btn.primary { background:#ea580c; color:#fff; border-color:#ea580c; }
    code { background:#f3f4f6; padding:.25rem .5rem; border-radius:6px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="badge">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 7L9 18l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      ¡Pago completado!
    </div>

    <h1>Gracias por tu compra</h1>
    <p class="muted">Tu pedido ha sido confirmado. En breve recibirás un correo con los detalles.</p>

    <div class="row grid">
      <div class="muted">ID de checkout</div>
      <div><code><%= params[:checkoutId] %></code></div>

      <% if params[:amount] %>
        <div class="muted">Total</div>
        <div>Q<%= params[:amount] %></div>
      <% end %>

      <% if params[:product] %>
        <div class="muted">Producto</div>
        <div><%= params[:product] %></div>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <div class="btns">
      <% if params[:receipt_url] %>
        <a class="btn" href="<%= params[:receipt_url] %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ver recibo</a>
      <% end %>
      <a class="btn primary" href="/">Volver a la tienda</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
